電影在全國約400塊銀幕上映。上映頭兩天，觀影人次已達80萬5350人，票房收入超過10.5億[[日圓|日圓]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.varietyjapan.com/news/movie_dom/2k1u7d000004wz6k.html|script-title=ja:『花男ファイナル』2日で10億突破|publisher=Variety Japan|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2009-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224134103/http://www.varietyjapan.com/news/movie_dom/2k1u7d000004wz6k.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 連續三週成為日本電影票房冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tokyograph.com/news/id-3517|title=HYD tops box office for third straight week|date=2008-07-15|publisher=Tokyograph|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2009-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090608195330/http://www.tokyograph.com/news/id-3517|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-14/japanese-box-office-june-28-29-hanadan-final-at-no.1|title=Japanese Box Office, June 28–29: HanaDan Final at #1|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2008-07-14|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2010-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100222100056/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-14/japanese-box-office-june-28-29-hanadan-final-at-no.1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-17/japanese-box-office-july-5-6-hanadan-stays-at-no.1|title=Japanese Box Office, July 5–6: HanaDan Stays at #1|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2008-07-17|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105074627/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-17/japanese-box-office-july-5-6-hanadan-stays-at-no.1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-21/japanese-box-office-july-12-13-hanadan-3rd-no.1-week|title=Japanese Box Office, July 12–13: HanaDan's 3rd #1 Week|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2008-07-21|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2012-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120525011952/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-07-21/japanese-box-office-july-12-13-hanadan-3rd-no.1-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>，連續十週票房收入高踞前十位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-08-11/japanese-box-office-august-2-3-ponyo-3rd-week-at-no.1|title=Japanese Boz Office, August 2–3: Ponyo's 3rd Week at #1|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2008-08-11|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2012-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822114638/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-08-11/japanese-box-office-august-2-3-ponyo-3rd-week-at-no.1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終票房收入高達77.5億日元，是2008年度日本電影票房收入亞軍，僅次於[[動畫電影|動畫電影]]《[[崖上的波妞|崖上的波妞]]》，因此也是該年度日本票房收入最高的真人電影。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.varietyjapan.com/news/movie_dom/2k1u7d00000gyv1d.html|script-title=ja:2008年作品別興行収入ベスト15|publisher=Variety Japan|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2009-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090125001924/http://www.varietyjapan.com/news/movie_dom/2k1u7d00000gyv1d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

